{"_id":"1b5d8fc7b13f8501","name":"Agumon's Share","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"food","target":"tamer","timing":"outside-combat","cost":{"digidollars":0,"realMoney":0,"special":"Loot only"},"quantity":1,"effect":"Counts as a meal for the Tamer. Prevents hunger. Restores 14 HP and grants +2 to all Courage-based skill rolls for the current session.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"+14 HP. +2 to all Courage-based skill rolls this session."}}
{"_id":"2e7d627ee089131b","name":"Digital Hazard Seal","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"supply","target":"both","timing":"basic-action","cost":{"digidollars":200,"realMoney":0,"special":""},"quantity":1,"effect":"Once as a Basic Action, apply this seal to one Digimon — ally or enemy — within 1 space. If applied to an ally it suppresses one status effect affecting them for two rounds (does not remove it — suspends it). If applied to an enemy make a Sincerity check DN 12. On a success the enemy's attack bonus is reduced by 2 for two rounds. On a failure the seal has no effect. The seal crumbles after use.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"Ally: suspends 1 status effect for 2 rounds. Enemy: Sincerity DN 12, -2 attack for 2 rounds on success. Range 1. Single use."}}
{"_id":"3e732c0c21eb59fe","name":"Digisoul Booster","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"supply","target":"tamer","timing":"basic-action","cost":{"digidollars":120,"realMoney":0,"special":""},"quantity":1,"effect":"Once as a Basic Action, use on the Tamer with the Marcus class tree. Until the end of the current encounter their Brawl checks for Fight Alongside have their DN reduced by 2. The booster is consumed on use.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"Marcus class only. Reduces Fight Alongside Brawl check DN by 2 until end of encounter. Single use."}}
{"_id":"4c9b0c836378996e","name":"Yggdrasil Access Key","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"equipment","target":"tamer","timing":"basic-action","cost":{"digidollars":0,"realMoney":0,"special":"Loot only — cannot be purchased"},"quantity":1,"effect":"Once per session as a Basic Action, interface this key with any terminal or data structure in the Digital World. Make an Archive check DN 15. On a success the GM reveals one piece of hidden information about the Digital World's current state — a system function, a locked area's contents, or what Yggdrasil is actively working on. On a failure the attempt fails and the key must cool down before it can be used again.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"1/session. Archive check DN 15. Failure: key cannot be used again until next session."}}
