{"_id":"a1ba446258b64948","name":"Stolen DATS Badge","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"equipment","target":"tamer","timing":"basic-action","cost":{"digidollars":0,"realMoney":0,"special":"Loot only — cannot be purchased"},"quantity":1,"effect":"As a Basic Action, present this badge to bluff your way past low-level DATS checkpoints or convince Digimon that you have official authority. Make a Broadcast check DN 11. On a success the bluff holds for this scene. On a failure you are identified and the GM determines the consequence. Does not work on DATS agents who know the bearer personally.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"Broadcast check DN 11. Fails against agents who know the bearer. One scene per use."}}
